1. *Pustimo* ovu temu i razgovarajmo o nečem drugom. (Let's drop this topic and talk about something else.)
2. Da *pustimo* to? (Shall we leave that?)
3. Učiniću sve što mogu da *pustim* te brigu. (I will do all I can to relieve you of that worry.)
4. *Pustimo* da se to desi. (Let it happen.)
5. Da *pustimo* prošlost i nastavimo dalje? (Shall we leave the past behind and move forward?)